00:34:51.289 --> 00:34:52.689
NAGI: Eh, bagaimana kalau permen?

00:34:52.724 --> 00:34:55.158
Katakan saja pada mereka untuk pulang.

00:34:55.193 --> 00:34:56.893
-Baiklah. -(terengah-engah) Langit!

00:34:56.928 --> 00:34:58.294
-(terkesiap) -Hah?

00:34:58.329 --> 00:35:00.363
♪ ♪

